{"tid":512361,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港各類偶像討論區（5）-粉紅是票和靈魂的顏色","createTime":"2017-12-28T11:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T11:50:50.000Z","uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8b296db7637f4d9514a964bcbc8cfca4ae9fd6","tid":512361,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"呢個post係俾大家討論一啲香港比較少人識或者另類嘅アイドル，所有除咗出面已經有post嘅idol group都可以傾，如果你有咩group想介紹，都可以嚟呢度講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\nQ:XXX可唔可以喺依到講<br />\nA:如上，只要出面冇post都可以喺到講<br />\n<br />\nQ: XX歌手真係好正<br />\nA: 日本偶像不同明星，俊男美女歌手於日本並唔叫偶像<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咩叫地下idol? <br />\nA: 叫地下係因為地下idol 一般都喺livehouse表演，而livehouse經常都設喺地下，並唔係尺度好低或者唔見得光嘅意思<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁地元idol呢？<br />\nA: 比較少出所在地區及/或以所在地區為主要image嘅idol<br />\n<br />\nQ: 日本偶像係咪都係靚妹仔着裙唱歌跳舞？<br />\nA: 日本偶像有好多種，有Metal風，王道風，Rock風等等，而根據唔同嘅廠牌、所在地亦有唔同嘅風格，緊有一款啱你心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n現時亦無限期為開個香港嘅アイドル界隈招生，有興趣留個言一齊去撞場踢館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n誠邀9up/叫春，問嘢都得，識得ヲタク朋友叫佢入黎吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5220df50e5c9f17e87f9cd54ea2562fff4e3025","tid":512361,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baa87547ad84fce581d8761ecb918fa0214cd38","tid":512361,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bcf47a896333c078628386d0019bca64b0b78e","tid":512361,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"個題寫左香港 開唔開個新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\"